Package: CERMBweather
Title: Functions to query BOM weather station data in a PostgreSQL database
Version: 0.5.1
Date: 2021-08-18
Authors@R: c(
  person("Hamish", "Clarke", email = "hamishc@uow.edu.au", role = c("aut")),
  person("Michael", "Bedward", email = "michael.bedward@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")) )
Description: Developed by the Centre for Environmental Risk Management
  of Bushfires, University of Wollongong (Australia) to query weather 
  data, provided by the Australian Bureau of Meteorology, stored in a PostgreSQL database.
